data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
FusionLeaf Studio (FLS) is a preconfigured distribution of Nginx, PHP, and MySQL. Use the Basic or Advanced tabs to control and monitor the services required for the FusionLeaf CMS.
Use the controls to below to quickly start and stop the following components: Ngnix - Web Server FastCGI (PHP) - Gateway Interface MySQL - Database Memcached - Caching System
